6.6 Limitations
The AI/ML component requires an internet connection and access to the Cohere API. API usage may also be limited by free-tier call limits. Another limitation is that general-purpose embeddings may not fully understand specialized biomedical vocabulary, especially very technical research terms. The semantic score should therefore support the rule-based score, not replace it.

6.7 Future Improvements
Future versions could improve the AI/ML component by using biomedical-specific embeddings trained on PubMed abstracts or research papers. The system could also collect user feedback on successful and unsuccessful matches, then use that feedback to adjust weights or train a supervised machine learning model.



